<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<!--
  Sample: TPEG2 TFP Persistent Location Store (partialRepository).

  Predefined Location Set: carries the stable parts of multi-part TFP messages:
    - Master message  (optionMMCMasterLink) — announces which parts exist
    - Part 1          (optionMMCPartLink, partID=1) — location reference

  Part 2 (flow status) is transmitted separately in tpeg-tfp.xml and
  is correlated via the shared mmc:messageID.

  Two sample locations are included:
    - 78746043  TMC 37307 + OpenLR linear reference
    - 78865458  TMC 25650 + OpenLR linear reference
-->
